Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}宛如传达被托付的爱一般
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}生きて　生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}活下去 活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}命をつなぐよ　それが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}将生命的灯火传承下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}いま　いま　守るべき
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}那就是我现在该守护的东西
