Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}活下去 活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}命をつなぐよ　それが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fad(0,400)\an9}将生命的灯火传承下去
